commit.message:
configure.ac (TARGETDIR): Add missing blank lines.

2009-06-16  Andrew Haley  <aph@redhat.com>

	* configure.ac (TARGETDIR): Add missing blank lines.
	* configure: Regenerate.

From-SVN: r148538
